                    "text": "3. Add new code SpyEffect.RevealPowerSituation=yes so when we infiltrate power plant, when we click on it, we would know how much power enemy has. It should be exactly like we clikc on our own power plant to display ,,Power=xxx (amount)\"\r\n", 
